name: Bitcoin Baphomet
description: Bitcoin Baphomet, Inspired by T. C. Mays The Crypto Anarchists Manifesto and Eliphas Levis Baphomet drawing But instead of goats head it's masked privacy extremist holding Bitcoin in one hand and picking decentralised blockchain net with other hand, and the same as crypto has the bright and the dark side, she has tits and evil hairy legs... Yes, the spectre is haunting modern world
collection_description: SuperRare makes it easy to create, sell, and collect rare digital art. SuperRare's smart contract platform allows artists to release limited-edition digital artwork tracked on the blockchain, making the pieces rare, verified, and collectible. Filter the crypto art world's best selling works by artist name, creation type, and year of birth on OpenSea.
